data.description: Brand New Brick Kingsley Home plan from Essex Homes in the prestigious Woodcreek Farms. Awesome open floor plan walking distance to Catawba Elementary School. Guest bedroom and full bathroom downstairs makes a great mother-in-law suite! Kitchen includes kitchen island and large open area with huge walk in pantry and dining room off the kitchen. Great for entertaining! Hardwoods in dining, kitchen and family room. Upstairs boasts 4 full bedrooms Plus a bonus making this a true 5 bedroom with bonus room. Owner's suite boasts two separate walk in closets, tiled bathroom with 5 foot tile shower w/bench. Bonus room would be a great teen hangout, man cave or 2nd family room. All this and more in the gorgeous Woodcreek Farms community. Energy Efficient and qualifies for the SCE&G discounted Rate 6!!
